text: Ðis is þara X hida boc æt cleran þe Eadred cing gæbocodæ Ælfsigæ biscopæ feower manna dæg.
And æftær heora daga into ealdan mynstræ.
Ærest of hilda hlæwe on hunig wege.
Andlang weges on brege stipe stan.
Of þan stane on scæp wescan andlang sceapwascan on aleburnan.
Andlang aleburnan on bæueres broces heafde on coferan treowe on þa bradan ac.
Of þære bradan ac on stuteres hylle <niþewearde> on stuteres hylle on wearð setl.
Of weard setle on wiþig grafas.
Of wiþig grafan on scip del of scip delle on cyp manna delle.
Andlang weges eft east on hyldan hlew.
